Social and Business Impact
Social Impact
Helps identify high-risk patient groups.
Supports early awareness of heart disease.
Improves understanding of health trends.
Encourages preventive healthcare practices.
Assists healthcare professionals in making informed decisions.
Business Impact
Enables hospitals to analyze patient data efficiently.
Supports data-driven healthcare planning.
Reduces manual reporting efforts.
Improves operational efficiency through visualization.
Assists government organizations in health policy planning.